{
  "stem": "1641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later on, when the snow was really big, I bought a pair of shoes, which saved my life later on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- I changed all my brothel tickets, six tickets, and cigarettes for-- for food, jumper, and-- and boots.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then one day, the SS man said, I need somebody to translate to other languages, because a big transport of Dutch Jews came in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could all speak English, and the French Jews, of course, French, and the Hungarians, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the-- the orders are given in German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I need somebody who speaks Hungarian, apart from German, and English and French.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I said, oh, I can do this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said, well, listen, you be careful, because if you're bluffing, I'll-- I'll test you very soon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You'll get shot if-- if you're telling me a lie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, no, I can do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All right, we'll see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he gave an order-- stand up here or stand up there, and I translated it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my first big job-- I got a new armband.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was still a part-time [NON-ENGLISH]-- bodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But main-- my main job was now interpreter to the SS of that building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We got our own SS man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my first job was, which was a pretty-- a very responsible job, in the evening, when all the workers came back from work-- dead tired, hungry, dirty, you know, from carrying cement or concrete blocks or working in the mines-- I met them all.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And all the sick people-- and nearly everybody was sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
